      "id": 3,
      "text": "Village leaders set a strict zoning rule requiring minimum two‑acre lots for single‑family homes, keeping Pomona’s rural feel intact.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        5
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
